data.name: chkGeneral_MewExclusiveTutor.ToolTip
data.value:
In vanilla Pokémon, Mew is able to learn every TM, HM, TR and Tutor Move except those exclusive to a particular Pokémon or group of Pokémon, such as Draco Meteor and Secret Sword.
Checking this setting, will allow Mew to learn those exclusive moves.

data.name: chkNewDefines.ToolTip
data.value:
In pokeemerald-expansion, certain move defines were updated to match their current names, such as VICE_GRIP -> VISE_GRIP or FAINT_ATTACK -> FEINT_ATTACK .
Unchecking this box will use default pokeemerald's labels.
